com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.dynamictype
Interface DynamicPaletteEntry

public interface DynamicPaletteEntry

A representation of the model object 'Dynamic Palette Entry'. The specification of a dynamic palette entry

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Id
  • Kind
  • Label
  • Large Icon
  • Path
  • Small Icon
  • Template URI

See Also:
DynamictypePackage.getDynamicPaletteEntry()
